}} [[coins]], or {{NoCoins|{{#var:wew}}*2}} with the full [[Rogue equipment|rogue's outfit]]. At maximum efficiency of 3,000 pickpockets per hour without any failure, this equates to {{NoCoins|{{#var:wew}}*2*3000 round 1}} coins per hour.

[[Ironman Mode|Ironmen]] looking for herb seeds can expect up to 60 high level seeds ([[ranarr seed|ranarr]] or higher) per hour at maximum efficiency.

Before reaching 85 Farming, players can expect a decreased drop rate for [[ranarr seed]]s, [[snapdragon seed]]s and [[torstol seed]]s.{{CiteTwitter|author=Mod Ash|url=https://twitter.com/JagexAsh/status/1400868684474765314|date=4 June 2021|archiveurl=https://archive.is/587zW|archivedate=6 September 2021|quote=}}{{CiteTwitter|author=Mod Ash|url=https://twitter.com/JagexAsh/status/1460070685678747652|date=15 November 2021|archiveurl=https://archive.md/5xvrY|archivedate=27 November 2021|quote=}}

