==Pickpocketing==
===Pickpocket chance===
The chance of successfully pickpocketing a Master Farmer scales between 91/256 at level 1, and 241/256 at level 99.{{CiteTwitter|author=Mod Kieren|url=https://twitter.com/JagexKieren/status/691576301296164865|date=25 January 2016|archiveurl=https://archive.is/nVSVe|archivedate=30 May 2020|quote=Master farmers: 90/255 at lv1, 240/255 at 99.}}

With the multiplicative +10% pickpocketing bonus from the [[Hard Ardougne Diary]], players will stop failing to pickpocket them at level 94 Thieving.

